<style>
.ams-hub-wrapper {
  --ams-navy: #1a2b5e;
  --ams-blue: #1a2b5e;
  --ams-sky:  #c8102e;
  --ams-sand: #f1f5f9;
  --ams-white: #ffffff;
  --ams-gray: #f8fafc;

  font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
  color: var(--ams-navy);
  line-height: 1.6;
  width: 100%;
  overflow-x: hidden;
  margin-bottom: 80px;
}
.ams-hub-wrapper * { box-sizing: border-box; }

.ams-section { padding: 40px 20px; width: 100%; }
.ams-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }

.ams-spacer { height: 60px; width: 100%; }
@media (max-width: 768px) { .ams-spacer { height: 40px; } }

.ams-hub-wrapper h1,
.ams-hub-wrapper h2.ams-main-title {
  font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
  font-weight: 800;
  text-align: left;
  color: var(--ams-navy);
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  letter-spacing: -1.5px;
  line-height: 1.1;
  border-left: none;
  padding-left: 0;
  margin-top: 10px;
}

.ams-hub-wrapper h2 {
  font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-top: 35px;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  color: var(--ams-navy);
  text-align: left;
  line-height: 1.3;
  border-left: 5px solid var(--ams-sky);
  padding-left: 15px;
}

.ams-hub-wrapper h3 {
  font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 1.8rem);
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  color: var(--ams-navy);
  margin-top: 20px;
  border-left: 5px solid var(--ams-sky);
  padding-left: 15px;
  line-height: 1.3;
}

.ams-card-title {
  font-size: 1.3rem !important;
  font-weight: 700 !important;
  margin: 0 0 12px 0 !important;
  border-left: none !important;
  padding-left: 0 !important;
  color: var(--ams-navy);
  display: block;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.ams-hub-wrapper p {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: #475569;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
}

.ams-subhead {
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  color: #475569;
  margin-bottom: 35px;
  max-width: 900px;
  text-align: left;
}

/* --- Answer Capsule --- */
.ams-answer-capsule {
  background: var(--ams-gray);
  border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
  border-left: 5px solid var(--ams-sky);
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 24px 28px;
  margin: 0 0 50px 0;
}
.ams-capsule-heading {
  font-size: 1.05rem !important;
  font-weight: 700 !important;
  color: var(--ams-navy) !important;
  margin-bottom: 8px !important;
}
.ams-answer-capsule p {
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: #475569;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.ams-capsule-programs {
  margin-bottom: 0 !important;
  color: #64748b !important;
}

/* --- Options Grid --- */
.ams-options-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  gap: 30px;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}

@media (min-width: 650px) and (max-width: 1023px) {
  .ams-options-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
}

@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .ams-options-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
}

.ams-option-card {
  background: white;
  padding: 40px 30px;
  border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
  border-bottom: 4px solid var(--ams-sky);
  border-radius: 12px;
  text-align: left;
  transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: space-between;
  height: 100%;
}

.ams-option-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-8px);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(26, 43, 94, 0.08);
}

/* --- Icons --- */
.ams-icon-box {
  width: 65px;
  height: 65px;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
  border-radius: 14px;
  background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ffffff, #f1f5f9);
  box-shadow: 4px 4px 10px #e2e8f0, -4px -4px 10px #ffffff;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

.ams-lux-svg {
  width: 32px;
  height: 32px;
  fill: url(#amsGradient);
}

/* --- Buttons --- */
.ams-btn-text {
  color: var(--ams-navy);
  font-weight: 700;
  text-decoration: none;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ams-sky);
  padding-bottom: 4px;
  align-self: flex-start;
  margin-top: 20px;
  transition: color 0.2s;
}
.ams-btn-text:hover { color: var(--ams-sky); }

.ams-btn-primary, .ams-btn-outline {
  padding: 18px 28px;
  font-weight: 800;
  text-decoration: none;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  border-radius: 10px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  transition: all 0.3s;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  width: 100%;
  letter-spacing: 0.8px;
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .ams-btn-primary, .ams-btn-outline { width: auto; min-width: 300px; }
}

/* --- Discreet App CTA --- */
.ams-auth-btn.primary {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #475569;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  text-decoration: none;
  padding: 8px 16px;
  background-color: var(--ams-gray);
  border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
  border-radius: 6px;
  margin-top: -15px;
  margin-bottom: 30px;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
.ams-auth-btn.primary:hover {
  background-color: var(--ams-blue);
  color: var(--ams-white);
  border-color: var(--ams-blue);
}

/* --- Limit Box --- */
.ams-limit-box {
  background: var(--ams-navy);
  padding: 50px 40px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  margin: 80px 0;
  text-align: center;
  border-top: 5px solid var(--ams-sky);
}
.ams-limit-box h4 {
  color: var(--ams-sky);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  font-weight: 800;
  text-align: center;
}
.ams-limit-box p {
  color: #fff !important;
  margin: 0 auto;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  text-align: center;
  max-width: 780px;
}

/* --- Final CTA --- */
.ams-cta-wrapper {
  background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(10, 15, 28, 0.97), rgba(10, 15, 28, 0.94)), url('/images/american-mortgage-services-tampa.webp');
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  background-color: var(--ams-navy);
  text-align: center;
  padding: 100px 30px;
  margin-top: 40px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  color: var(--ams-white);
}

.ams-cta-inner h2 {
  color: var(--ams-white) !important;
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  border-left: none;
  padding-left: 0;
  text-align: center;
}

.ams-cta-inner p {
  color: #cbd5e1 !important;
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto 40px auto;
}

.ams-btn-container {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 20px;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-top: 40px;
}
@media (min-width: 768px) { .ams-btn-container { flex-direction: row; } }

.ams-btn-primary {
  background: var(--ams-sky);
  color: var(--ams-white) !important;
  border: 2px solid var(--ams-sky);
}
.ams-btn-primary:hover {
  background: #a50d26;
  border-color: #a50d26;
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.ams-btn-outline {
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--ams-white) !important;
  border: 2px solid var(--ams-white);
}
.ams-btn-outline:hover {
  background: var(--ams-white);
  color: var(--ams-navy) !important;
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

/* --- NMLS Disclosure --- */
.ams-nmls { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 30px; line-height: 1.6; }
</style>

<div class="ams-hub-wrapper">

  <svg width="0" height="0" style="position: absolute;" aria-hidden="true">
    <defs>
      <linearGradient id="amsGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
        <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#1a2b5e;stop-opacity:1" />
        <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#c8102e;stop-opacity:1" />
      </linearGradient>
    </defs>
  </svg>

  <div class="ams-section">
    <div class="ams-inner">

      <!-- ANSWER CAPSULE -->
      <div class="ams-answer-capsule">
        <p class="ams-capsule-heading">Mortgage Options Built Around Your Situation</p>
        <p>American Mortgage Services helps borrowers compare loan options for buying, building, refinancing, investing, and using VA benefits.</p>
        <p class="ams-capsule-programs">Popular options include: VA, FHA, USDA, Conventional, Jumbo, Construction, DSCR, Bank Statement, and Refinance loans.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- SECTION 1: Home Purchase -->
      <h2>Home Purchase Programs</h2>
      <p class="ams-subhead">Most buyers start here. These programs cover the most common purchase situations regardless of where you're buying. Depending on your scenario, you may qualify for more than one option.</p>

      <a href="/loan-officers/" class="ams-auth-btn primary">Start Your Application</a>

      <div class="ams-options-grid">
        <div class="ams-option-card">
          <div class="ams-icon-box">
            <svg class="ams-lux-svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10,20V14H14V20H19V12H22L12,3L2,12H5V20H10Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="ams-card-title">Buy With Low Money Down</span>
            <p>Conventional financing starting at 3% down for qualified buyers. Ideal if you have solid credit and want to keep more cash in your pocket after closing.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/programs/conventional-loans" class="ams-btn-text">Explore This Option &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="ams-option-card">
          <div class="ams-icon-box">
            <svg class="ams-lux-svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4,10H8V21H4V10M10,10H14V21H10V10M16,10H20V21H16V10M12,1L2,6V8H22V6L12,1Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="ams-card-title">Credit Challenges: You May Still Qualify</span>
            <p>Government-backed financing with flexible credit guidelines and low down payment requirements. Many buyers with less-than-perfect credit may qualify. Talk with a loan officer about your situation.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/programs/fha-loans" class="ams-btn-text">Explore This Option &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="ams-option-card">
          <div class="ams-icon-box">
            <svg class="ams-lux-svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M7.41,8.58L12,13.17L16.59,8.58L18,10L12,16L6,10L7.41,8.58M12,2A10,10 0 0,1 22,12A10,10 0 0,1 12,22A10,10 0 0,1 2,12A10,10 0 0,1 12,2M12,4A8,8 0 0,0 4,12A8,8 0 0,0 12,20A8,8 0 0,0 20,12A8,8 0 0,0 12,4Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="ams-card-title">First-Time Buyer Programs</span>
            <p>Down payment assistance programs and first-time buyer loan options may be available depending on your state, income, and purchase price. Subject to program availability, income limits, and lender guidelines.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/programs/first-time-homebuyer-loans" class="ams-btn-text">Explore This Option &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ams-spacer"></div>

      <!-- SECTION 2: Military and VA -->
      <h2>Military and VA Loans</h2>
      <p class="ams-subhead">We specialize in zero-down options for those who have served, along with rural financing and jumbo programs for larger purchases. Talk with a loan officer about your benefit entitlement and eligibility.</p>

      <a href="/loan-officers/" class="ams-auth-btn primary">Start Your Application</a>

      <div class="ams-options-grid">
        <div class="ams-option-card">
          <div class="ams-icon-box">
            <svg class="ams-lux-svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12,15.39L8.24,17.66L9.23,13.38L5.91,10.5L10.29,10.13L12,6.09L13.71,10.13L18.09,10.5L14.77,13.38L15.76,17.66L12,15.39M22,9.24L14.81,8.63L12,2L9.19,8.63L2,9.24L7.45,13.97L5.82,21L12,17.27L18.18,21L16.54,13.97L22,9.24Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="ams-card-title">Veterans: Zero Down</span>
            <p>Eligible veterans and active-duty service members may qualify for zero-down home financing with no private mortgage insurance. Talk with a loan officer about your VA benefit entitlement.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/programs/va-loans" class="ams-btn-text">Explore VA Benefits &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="ams-option-card">
          <div class="ams-icon-box">
            <svg class="ams-lux-svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12,21L15.6,11L12,2L8.4,11L12,21M13,22H11V23H13V22M15,13L21.5,10.5L18.5,4L12.5,10L15,13M11.5,10L5.5,4L2.5,10.5L9,13L11.5,10Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="ams-card-title">Zero Down in Rural Areas</span>
            <p>USDA rural housing programs offer zero-down financing in eligible areas outside major metro zones. Property and income eligibility requirements apply. Ask us if your target area qualifies.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/programs/usda-loans/" class="ams-btn-text">Check Eligibility &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="ams-option-card">
          <div class="ams-icon-box">
            <svg class="ams-lux-svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15,14V11H18V9H15V6H13V9H10V7H8V9H5V11H8V14H5V16H8V19H10V16H13V19H15V16H18V14H15M13,14H10V11H13V14Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="ams-card-title">Buying Above the Conforming Limit</span>
            <p>Financing for high-value properties that exceed conventional loan limits. Ideal for buyers in premium markets. Subject to credit, income, and reserve requirements.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/programs/jumbo-loans" class="ams-btn-text">Explore Jumbo Options &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ams-spacer"></div>

      <!-- SECTION 3: Investment and Self-Employed -->
      <h2>Investment and Self-Employed Mortgages</h2>
      <p class="ams-subhead">Non-traditional income shouldn't stop you from buying. We work with investors, entrepreneurs, and self-employed borrowers who need flexible qualification paths.</p>

      <a href="/loan-officers/" class="ams-auth-btn primary">Start Your Application</a>

      <div class="ams-options-grid">
        <div class="ams-option-card">
          <div class="ams-icon-box">
            <svg class="ams-lux-svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15,11V5L12,2L9,5V7H3V21H21V11H15M7,19H5V17H7V19M7,15H5V13H7V15M7,11H5V9H7V11M13,19H11V17H13V19M13,15H11V13H13V15M13,11H11V9H13V11M13,7H11V5H13V7M19,19H17V17H19V19M19,15H17V13H19V15" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="ams-card-title">Build Your Rental Portfolio</span>
            <p>Financing strategies for investors acquiring single-family rentals, duplexes, and small multifamily properties. Talk with a loan officer about leverage options based on your portfolio and goals.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/programs/investor-loans" class="ams-btn-text">Explore Investor Options &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="ams-option-card">
          <div class="ams-icon-box">
            <svg class="ams-lux-svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16,6L18.29,8.29L13.41,13.17L9.41,9.17L2,16.59L3.41,18L9.41,12L13.41,16L19.71,9.71L22,12V6H16Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="ams-card-title">Qualify on Cash Flow, Not Income</span>
            <p>Investor loan programs that use the property's rental income to qualify, not your personal tax returns. Subject to DSCR minimums, property type, and lender program guidelines.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/programs/investor-loans" class="ams-btn-text">Explore Cash Flow Loans &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="ams-option-card">
          <div class="ams-icon-box">
            <svg class="ams-lux-svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M13,9V3.5L18.5,9M6,2C4.89,2 4,2.89 4,4V20C4,21.11 4.89,22 6,22H18C19.11,22 20,21.11 20,20V8L14,2H6M11,15V12H12V15H13V16H12V19H11V16H10V15H11Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="ams-card-title">Self-Employed? Use Your Deposits</span>
            <p>Bank statement programs let self-employed borrowers qualify using 12-24 months of business or personal deposits instead of tax returns. Subject to credit and lender program guidelines.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/programs/bank-statement-loans" class="ams-btn-text">Explore Bank Statement Loans &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- LIMIT BOX -->
      <div class="ams-limit-box">
        <h4>The American Mortgage Services Difference</h4>
        <p>
          Licensed across six states and serving borrowers since our founding. NMLS #259805. We deliver wholesale mortgage rates with the personal service of a local team: faster closings, lower costs, and a loan officer who answers the phone.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- SECTION 4: Construction and Renovation -->
      <h2>Construction and Renovation Loans</h2>
      <p class="ams-subhead">Building new or buying a fixer-upper? We have programs that finance the construction or renovation alongside the purchase, depending on your scenario and the property type.</p>

      <a href="/loan-officers/" class="ams-auth-btn primary">Start Your Application</a>

      <div class="ams-options-grid">
        <div class="ams-option-card">
          <div class="ams-icon-box">
            <svg class="ams-lux-svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17,11V13H15V11H13V13H11V11H9V13H7V11H5V13H3V11H1V13V21H23V13V11H21V13H19V11H17M1,9V7H3V9H5V7H7V9H9V7H11V9H13V7H15V9H17V7H19V9H21V7H23V9H1V9Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="ams-card-title">Finance Your Custom Build</span>
            <p>Construction loan programs that fund your custom build in stages as the work progresses. Talk with a loan officer about lot ownership, builder approval, and draw schedules that fit your project.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/programs/conventional-loans" class="ams-btn-text">Talk to a Loan Officer &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="ams-option-card">
          <div class="ams-icon-box">
            <svg class="ams-lux-svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22.7,19L13.6,9.9C14.5,7.6 14,4.9 12.1,3C10.1,1 7.1,0.6 4.7,1.7L9,6L6,9L1.6,4.7C0.4,7.1 0.9,10.1 2.9,12.1C4.8,14 7.5,14.5 9.8,13.6L18.9,22.7C19.3,23.1 19.9,23.1 20.3,22.7L22.6,20.4C23.1,20 23.1,19.3 22.7,19Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="ams-card-title">Buy a Fixer-Upper, Finance the Repairs</span>
            <p>Renovation loan programs combine the home purchase price and estimated repair costs into a single loan. Depending on your scenario, this may allow you to buy and improve a property with one closing.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/programs/renovation-loans" class="ams-btn-text">Explore Renovation Loans &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="ams-option-card">
          <div class="ams-icon-box">
            <svg class="ams-lux-svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12,17.27L18.18,21L16.54,13.97L22,9.24L14.81,8.62L12,2L9.19,8.62L2,9.24L7.45,13.97L5.82,21L12,17.27Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="ams-card-title">Build New With Zero Down</span>
            <p>Eligible veterans may be able to combine VA benefits with new construction financing. Subject to builder approval, VA entitlement, and lender program availability. Speak with a loan officer about your options.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/programs/va-loans" class="ams-btn-text">Explore VA Construction &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ams-spacer"></div>

      <!-- SECTION 5: Refinance and Equity -->
      <h2>Refinance and Equity</h2>
      <p class="ams-subhead">Already own a home? You may be able to lower your payment, change your term, or access your equity depending on your current loan balance, rate, and property value.</p>

      <a href="/loan-officers/" class="ams-auth-btn primary">Start Your Application</a>

      <div class="ams-options-grid">
